title: Uber Introduces Package Return Service
description: The ride-hailing and delivery company said it began offering the service to help people who find it annoying or time-consuming to ship return items.

title: Smiling Kids, Gorgeous Sunsets: Is It Photo Editing or Just Plain Lying?
description: AI blurs the line between photography and “fauxtography.” On Google’s new Pixel 8 phones, you can face swap for the perfect family portrait.

title: SoftBank's Son Says Artificial General Intelligence Will Soon Surpass Humans
description: “Take advantage of it or be left behind,” the CEO said at the investment company’s annual SoftBank World event.
